pageTitle: Claifying the new subscription system for Banner website | MyTrimbleNews.com
TableContextTimeStampAfterTable: {19289=I’ve had several people ask me questions about last week’s front page article on our move to a subscription-based website, effective Feb. 23. Don’t worry. If you’re a subscriber to The Trimble Banner, you’ll have access all news and other content at MyTrimbleNews.com. Access to the website is free for all of our print subscribers. But you will have to take a few quick steps to get registered, then you’ll be ready to use the digital version of the newspaper., 25009=Trimble Banner | circulation@mytrimblenews.com | 502-255-3205 P.O.
